        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Tire Investment, Recovery and Extension Act of 2009 or the TIRE Act of 2009<i><b>- </b></i>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow taxpayers who regularly use more than 100 vehicles a year in a trade or business (vehicle fleet operators) a tax credit for the purchase of new or retread tires made from recycled rubber. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
